{
  "book": 25,
  "chapter": 5,
  "sections": [
    {
      "type": "heading",
      "heading": "求耶和華垂憐"
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Remember, O Lord, what has befallen us; look, and see our disgrace! "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Remember, O Lord, what has befallen us; look, and see our disgrace!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 1,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Our inheritance has been turned over to strangers, our homes to foreigners. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Our inheritance has been turned over to strangers, our homes to foreigners."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 2,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "We have become orphans, fatherless; our mothers are like widows. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "We have become orphans, fatherless; our mothers are like widows."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 3,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "We must pay for the water we drink; the wood we get must be bought. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "We must pay for the water we drink; the wood we get must be bought."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 4,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Our pursuers are at our necks; we are weary; we are given no rest. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Our pursuers are at our necks; we are weary; we are given no rest."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 5,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "We have given the hand to Egypt, and to Assyria, to get bread enough. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "We have given the hand to Egypt, and to Assyria, to get bread enough."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 6,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Our fathers sinned, and are no more; and we bear their iniquities. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Our fathers sinned, and are no more; and we bear their iniquities."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 7,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Slaves rule over us; there is none to deliver us from their hand. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Slaves rule over us; there is none to deliver us from their hand."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 8,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "We get our bread at the peril of our lives, because of the sword in the wilderness. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "We get our bread at the peril of our lives, because of the sword in the wilderness."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 9,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Our skin is hot as an oven with the burning heat of famine. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Our skin is hot as an oven with the burning heat of famine."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 10,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Women are raped in Zion, young women in the towns of Judah. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Women are raped in Zion, young women in the towns of Judah."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 11,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Princes are hung up by their hands; no respect is shown to the elders. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Princes are hung up by their hands; no respect is shown to the elders."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 12,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Young men are compelled to grind at the mill, and boys stagger under loads of wood. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Young men are compelled to grind at the mill, and boys stagger under loads of wood."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 13,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The old men have left the city gate, the young men their music. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The old men have left the city gate, the young men their music."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 14,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The joy of our hearts has ceased; our dancing has been turned to mourning. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The joy of our hearts has ceased; our dancing has been turned to mourning."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 15,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "The crown has fallen from our head; woe to us, for we have sinned! "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "The crown has fallen from our head; woe to us, for we have sinned!"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 16,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "For this our heart has become sick, for these things our eyes have grown dim, "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "For this our heart has become sick, for these things our eyes have grown dim,"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 17,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "for Mount Zion which lies desolate; jackals prowl over it. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "for Mount Zion which lies desolate; jackals prowl over it. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 18,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "But you, O Lord, reign forever; your throne endures to all generations. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "But you, O Lord, reign forever; your throne endures to all generations."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 19,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Why do you forget us forever, why do you forsake us for so many days? "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Why do you forget us forever, why do you forsake us for so many days?"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 20,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "Restore us to yourself, O Lord, that we may be restored! Renew our days as of old— "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Restore us to yourself, O Lord, that we may be restored! Renew our days as of old—"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "Restore us to yourself, O Lord, that we may be restored! Renew our days as of old—"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 21,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": " "
        },
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": true,
          "verseText": "unless you have utterly rejected us, and you remain exceedingly angry with us. "
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "line-quote",
      "contents": [
        {
          "verseNum": 22,
          "hasVerseLabel": false,
          "verseText": "unless you have utterly rejected us, and you remain exceedingly angry with us."
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}